iCoder
iCoder is a blog platform built entirely using Bootstrap. It provides a clean and responsive interface for users to read and share blog posts on various topics. This project is designed to demonstrate the power of Bootstrap in creating a fully functional and visually appealing web application.
Features
Responsive design with Bootstrap 4/5.
Clean and modern user interface.
Blog post listing with categories and tags.
Search functionality to find posts.
Comment section for user interaction.
Easy to customize and expand.
Technologies Used
Bootstrap 4/5: For responsive design and layout.
HTML5: For structuring the content.
CSS3: For additional styling.
JavaScript: For interactivity and dynamic content.
